            <div class="definition">
                <h1>Disneybound</h1>
                <p>Wearing a fashionable outfit inspirped by a disney character using colorblocking, fun prints,
                and or accessories.</p>
                <p>The term was founded by Leslie Kay.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="definition">
                <h1>Match the Magic</h1>
                <p>A site created to help Disneybounders plan their next Disneybounds</p>
                <p>Search for characters sorted by {{#link-to "colors"}}Color{{/link-to}} or {{#link-to "movies"}}Movie{{/link-to}}.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
